imdb.plot outline: From pedigreed show dogs to prize mares, cows, cute and cuddly cats, and even angry bulls, the series follows the action-packed life of traveling vet Dr. Keri Hudson Reykdal, who's on the road 24/7 to care for 'all creatures big and small.' She's dedicated her life to animals - treating them, training them, and riding them in horse derbies - with one of the busiest and most unusual mobile veterinary units to roam the northern prairie.
